My dear X friends;
You are not my follower, we are a family and a team! And we all do great teamwork together!

I gained 1 MILLION  real followers in a short time.
Thank you for supporting me and being by my side! ❤️

I will tell you real motivation.

After my 850K account was closed in August 2022, I started posting on this account in October 2022.
And I gained 1 MILLION followers in 13 months.
I have never used fake interaction.
I never went viral with fake interactions.

I won people's hearts through hard work and by showing respect.
The key to success is respect.

Of course, gaining 1 million followers was never easy!

Some large accounts posted the videos I shared at the same time so that my account would not grow, so that I would not get any interaction and so that I would not gain followers.

But I didn't give up!
I challenged many people!
I said to myself that when I succeed, I'll make you take your hat off!  :))

And now I've done an incredible job!

If you're following me, you won't get lost with me. :)
The place I will take you is peace and humor and laughter.
There will always be things in my account that will be good for you.

I'm not a fake motivation. 
I'm the real motivation for you ...

Thank you for honoring me by supporting me ... ❤️❤️
